   Version 2.32    More keys                           October the 10th, 1993
                   GUS support
                   Bug in the loader fixed

       - You can now enable/disable also the channels 11-16 by pressing the
         number of the channel with alt.
       - Gravis Ultrasound now supported. Unfortunately, no bars nor power
         meters with it. Maybe in the future.. Anyway, no power meter would
         be needed, anyway -- playing with GUS takes approximately half a
         scanline in 486/33.. ;)
       - A bug in the loader part fixed. I don't know if it helps or not,
         but it's fixed now, anyway..

