   Version 2.0     Bugfixes                               March the 4th, 1993
                   More module formats
                   New outlook
                   Enhancements

       - Pro Audio Spectrum support did not work at all. Corrected.
       - Also other bugfixes, but I can't remember what..
       - Triton's Fast Tracker 6 and 8 channel module support added
       - Changed the screen into 50-line mode.
       - PMP now loads many modules to memory, so you can play multiple
         modules at the background (and it takes no more memory from DOS!)
       - Keyboard handler added, you can operate PMP also from DOS shell
       - PMP now supports an environment variable, PMP, in which you can
         save your preferred settings

